<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
    <title>Support Email Test - Debug</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            max-width: 800px;
            margin: 50px auto;
            padding: 20px;
        }
        .form-group {
            margin-bottom: 15px;
        }
        label {
            display: block;
            margin-bottom: 5px;
            font-weight: bold;
        }
        input[type="text"],
        input[type="email"],
        textarea {
            width: 100%;
            padding: 8px;
            border: 1px solid #ddd;
            border-radius: 4px;
        }
        textarea {
            height: 150px;
        }
        button {
            background-color: #0d78f2;
            color: white;
            padding: 10px 20px;
            border: none;
            border-radius: 4px;
            cursor: pointer;
        }
        button:hover {
            background-color: #0c6cd6;
        }
        .flash {
            padding: 10px;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            border-radius: 4px;
        }
        .flash.success {
            background-color: #d4edda;
            color: #155724;
        }
        .flash.error {
            background-color: #f8d7da;
            color: #721c24;
        }
        .debug {
            background: #f5f5f5;
            padding: 15px;
            margin-top: 20px;
            border-radius: 4px;
            font-size: 12px;
        }
        .file-info {
            background: #e8f4f8;
            padding: 10px;
            margin-top: 10px;
            border-radius: 4px;
            font-size: 14px;
        }
    </style>
    <script>
        function updateFileInfo() {
            const fileInput = document.getElementById('attachment');
            const fileInfo = document.getElementById('fileInfo');

            if (fileInput.files.length > 0) {
                const file = fileInput.files[0];
                fileInfo.innerHTML = `
                    <strong>Ausgewählte Datei:</strong><br>
                    Name: ${file.name}<br>
                    Typ: ${file.type}<br>
                    Größe: ${(file.size / 1024 / 1024).toFixed(2)} MB
                `;
                fileInfo.style.display = 'block';
            } else {
                fileInfo.style.display = 'none';
            }
        }
    </script>
</head>
<body>
    <h1>Support Email Test (mit Debug)</h1>

    {% if craft.app.session.hasFlash('success') %}
        <div class="flash success">
            {{ craft.app.session.getFlash('success') }}
        </div>
    {% endif %}

    {% if craft.app.session.hasFlash('error') %}
        <div class="flash error">
            {{ craft.app.session.getFlash('error') }}
        </div>
    {% endif %}

    <div class="debug">
        <strong>Debug-Info:</strong><br>
        Action-URL: <code>{{ actionUrl('diffbase/support/send-email') }}</code><br>
        Mailpit-URL: <a href="http://plugins.ddev.site:8026" target="_blank">http://plugins.ddev.site:8026</a><br>
        Temp-Pfad: <code>{{ craft.app.path.tempPath }}</code>
    </div>

    <form method="post" action="{{ actionUrl('diffbase/support/send-email') }}" enctype="multipart/form-data">
        {{ csrfInput() }}

        <div class="form-group">
            <label for="name">Name:</label>
            <input type="text" id="name" name="name" value="Test User" required>
        </div>

        <div class="form-group">
            <label for="email">E-Mail:</label>
            <input type="email" id="email" name="email" value="test@example.com" required>
        </div>

        <div class="form-group">
            <label for="message">Nachricht:</label>
            <textarea id="message" name="message" required>Dies ist eine Test-Nachricht mit Dateianhang.</textarea>
        </div>

        <div class="form-group">
            <label for="attachment">Anhang (optional):</label>
            <input type="file" id="attachment" name="attachment" onchange="updateFileInfo()">
            <div id="fileInfo" class="file-info" style="display:none;"></div>
        </div>

        <button type="submit">Senden</button>
    </form>

    <hr style="margin-top: 40px;">
    <h3>Wie finde ich den Anhang in Mailpit?</h3>
    <ol>
        <li>Öffne Mailpit: <a href="http://plugins.ddev.site:8026" target="_blank">http://plugins.ddev.site:8026</a></li>
        <li>Klicke auf die E-Mail in der Liste</li>
        <li>Suche nach dem Tab <strong>"Attachments"</strong> oder einem 📎 Symbol</li>
        <li>Die Anhänge werden dort aufgelistet und können heruntergeladen werden</li>
    </ol>
</body>
</html>
